premise_source_doc_sentence: The characters in the range U +048 A -- U +04 FF and the complete Cyrillic Supplement block  (  U +0500 - U +052 F  )  are additional letters for various languages that are written with Cyrillic script .

claim: The language of the Kassites was written with Cyrillic characters.
premise_source_doc_sentence: In order to enable drivers using their vehicle abroad , and in order to adhere to the Vienna Convention on Road Traffic , Ukrainian regular license plates use only those Cyrillic characters where the glyph resembles a letter from the Roman alphabet ; a total of 12 characters : A , B , E , I , K , M , H , O , P , C , T , X  )  .
